defOverlapWireReportFileName(25.10)        defOverlapWireReportFileName(25.10)

Name
       defOverlapWireReportFileName

Syntax
        defOverlapWireReportFileName <fileName>

       Type: String

       Default: NULL

       Reports  overlapping  wire segments in the specified file. The defOver-
       lapWireReportFileName variable can be used along with  the  defInShape-
       BasedDefFile variable.

